## Status Values

| Status | Meaning |
|---|---|
| `Pending` | Spec exists but work has not started. |
| `In Progress` | At least one task is being worked on or completed. |
| `Blocked` | Spec cannot continue due to dependency, decision or missing context. |
| `In Review` | Work is ready for human review. |
| `Done` | Required tasks and validation are complete. |
| `Archived` | Spec is no longer active but kept for reference. |

## Spec Types

`feature-change`, `bugfix`, `refactor`, `technical-debt`, `documentation`, `architecture-decision`, `discovery`, `audit`, `integration`, `migration`.

